"golden brown" is a song by the english rock band the stranglers. it was released as a 7" single in december 1981 in the united states and in january 1982 in the uk, on liberty. it was the second single released from the band's sixth album la folie. it peaked at no. 2 in the uk singles chart, the band's highest ever placing in that chart. in 2013, nme ranked the song number 488 on its list of the 500 greatest songs of all time.